{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"55d342a940","title":"周恩来对贺龙专案组请示报告的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cd481c5b92","index":0,"year":1970,"month":12,"day":3,"articleId":"55d342a940"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d0a2337495","name":"贺龙","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7a99cebe4e","name":"周恩来"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4f59ba4b21","type":"title","text":"周恩来对贺龙专案组请示报告的批示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"b88c51a3d9","type":"authors","text":"周恩来","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"123752d08d","type":"paragraph","text":"“东兴同志，这全部是公开文件，请你考虑是否需全部调阅。我记得在下放邓小平、谭震林时，已将两人从专案组撤消。现专案组既又重新提出查此人，可否先告专案组将邓小平以三反罪行、招降纳叛线索写一报告来，以便拟此查阅。周恩来。”","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"01f546eb21","type":"paragraph","text":"附一","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"f0063c80c3","type":"subtitle","text":"贺龙专案组的报告","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"049bcf25fa","type":"appellation","text":"康生、永胜、法宪、叶群同志：","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"6017362d46","type":"paragraph","text":"关于邓小平的三反罪行，招降纳叛等问题，经过调查，我们已掌握了不少材料和线索，但其中有些问题的核实和查证，还需要查阅一些档案材料。为此，我们拟到中央档案馆、中办机要室等单位查阅有关材料，并对必要的部分拍照取证。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"4a3f4932ee","type":"paragraph","text":"是否妥当，请批示。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"511d02dd19","type":"paragraph","text":"附：申请查档目录表。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"7481902139","type":"paragraph","text":" 贺龙专案组1970年11月28日","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"cf3927e92e","type":"paragraph","text":"附二：","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"30eb9367d2","type":"subtitle","text":"吴法宪对贺龙专案组报告的批示：","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"39e202e726","type":"paragraph","text":"可否查这些档案，呈请总理、汪东兴同志批示。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"},{"id":"452670f5a2","type":"paragraph","text":" 1970.11.30","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940"}],"page":{"id":"885f8d3812","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"55d342a940","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}